metadata.name: TROLL #1
metadata.description: The time of troubles has come. The time when vile, petty and evil goblins filled the world. Pitiful humans, elves and dwarves unsuccessfully try to resist them, but they do not succeed. Few people know, but there are rumors that very far away, beyond the mountains, lakes, rivers, seas and fields, there is a big city of trolls, about which nothing has been heard for a long time, but there is hope that the trolls will come to the aid of all living things and defeat the hated goblins.

attributes.value: T shirt I love killing goblins
